00:20:01,417 --> 00:20:03,000
What's-its-name.

277
00:20:03,125 --> 00:20:06,667
They have Fun World and Food Mall.

278
00:20:06,958 --> 00:20:09,917
Their chicken rice fills you up.

279
00:20:10,042 --> 00:20:13,250
Right, that's Silver City Centre.

280
00:20:13,417 --> 00:20:17,250
They serve huge bowls of rice.

281
00:20:18,458 --> 00:20:22,875
As for the place I most want to go, wow!

282
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:27,917
There, the sky is blue, clouds white, the trees tall…

283
00:20:28,042 --> 00:20:32,292
It is a world outside our world.

284
00:22:10,583 --> 00:22:13,458
Rise and shine, kiddo.

285
00:22:13,667 --> 00:22:14,667
Oh?

286
00:22:14,792 --> 00:22:16,958
Mother!

287
00:22:24,042 --> 00:22:26,125
Take some medicine and he'll be fine.

288
00:22:26,542 --> 00:22:29,250
Will he not what after the medicine?

289
00:22:29,292 --> 00:22:30,625
No!

290
00:22:30,792 --> 00:22:32,125
Need he not what for the medicine?

291
00:22:32,250 --> 00:22:33,875
No! I'll give him a shot.

292
00:22:34,292 --> 00:22:36,333
A shot?

293
