323
00:25:23,083 --> 00:25:24,750
Maldives?

324
00:25:24,958 --> 00:25:28,417
You said we would go once I got well.

325
00:25:28,583 --> 00:25:31,958
Maldives, where the trees tall and water bright…

326
00:25:32,083 --> 00:25:35,167
The world outside our world!

327
00:25:36,250 --> 00:25:38,667
Those words have flair.

328
00:25:38,833 --> 00:25:40,125
I am happy for you.

329
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:45,250
Mother, you promised…

330
00:25:45,458 --> 00:25:50,417
We'd go to Maldives once I got well.

331
00:25:50,583 --> 00:25:53,500
I meant once I get rich.

332
00:25:54,417 --> 00:25:58,708
No, that wasn't what you meant.

333
00:26:01,625 --> 00:26:06,083
You said we'd go once I got well.

334
00:26:07,042 --> 00:26:09,125
You promised!

335
00:26:09,958 --> 00:26:12,000
Now stop crying.

336
00:26:12,167 --> 00:26:13,708
We will go to Maldives.

337
00:26:13,875 --> 00:26:15,542
