379
00:33:55,833 --> 00:33:59,708
San San, when confirmed her winning…

380
00:33:59,833 --> 00:34:03,875
Told reporters that her result…

381
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:07,667
Helps prove that Hong Kong athletes are horrible…

382
00:34:09,292 --> 00:34:13,708
Excuse me, it should be "honourable".

383
00:34:13,875 --> 00:34:18,875
Hong Kong athletes are honourable athletes.

384
00:34:19,042 --> 00:34:21,000
End of special report.

385
00:34:25,042 --> 00:34:27,208
Then, mother seemed inspired.

386
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:30,500
Handsome, lucky, smart…

387
00:34:30,625 --> 00:34:32,458
So much for those plans.

388
00:34:32,958 --> 00:34:35,458
Now how about something physical?

389
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,917
"Looking for Logan"

390
00:34:36,958 --> 00:34:38,333
And so, while one dream lingers on…

391
00:34:38,500 --> 00:34:40,667
Another one begins.

392
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:43,417
"aka: How Does a Calf Become a Calf?"

393
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,417
It's about the Calf!

394
00:34:46,042 --> 00:34:47,583
I know it is not easy.

395
00:34:48,875 --> 00:34:51,583
I know it is not easy to find Logan.

396
00:34:52,875 --> 00:34:56,417
I know it is not easy for him to take me in.

397
00:34:59,708 --> 00:35:03,250
No matter how difficult this is…

398
00:35:03,417 --> 00:35:05,500
Logan will be my master!

399
00:35:05,833 --> 00:35:09,875
I shall get an Olympic medal!

400
00:35:14,250 --> 00:35:26,250
Cheung Chau!

401
00:35:26,792 --> 00:35:31,250
You raised San San, now you will raise me!

402
00:35:31,542 --> 00:35:34,542
When I receive my Olympic medal…

403
00:35:34,792 --> 00:35:38,375
I shall tell the world:

404
00:35:38,542 --> 00:35:42,083
HK athletes are honourable athletes!

405
00:35:49,792 --> 00:35:53,417
Cheung Chau, I finally make it here.

406
00:35:58,333 --> 00:36:05,583
I must kiss this holy land!

407
00:36:09,542 --> 00:36:13,667
Kiddo, this is Lamma Island.

408
00:36:14,667 --> 00:36:19,542
Lamma Island? Where Chow Yun Fat grew up?

409
00:36:29,708 --> 00:36:34,500
I came into hiding on this island…

410
00:36:35,292 --> 00:36:39,500
To stay away from the paparazzi.

411
00:36:39,667 --> 00:36:45,083
And so many kids came to seek me out.

412
00:36:45,250 --> 00:36:47,833
So I came to live here.

413
00:36:48,208 --> 00:36:50,083
You want me to be your master?

414
00:36:50,250 --> 00:36:51,917
Forget it!

415
00:36:52,250 --> 00:36:55,750
You city kids are all spoiled…

416
00:36:55,875 --> 00:36:57,708
Good for nothing!

417
00:36:57,833 --> 00:37:00,000
You want to get an Olympic medal too?

418
00:37:00,083 --> 00:37:02,000
Dream on!

419
00:37:05,333 --> 00:37:09,000
Kiddo, look!

420
00:37:15,375 --> 00:37:16,167
This calf…

421
00:37:16,333 --> 00:37:21,292
So thick, so strong!

422
00:37:21,417 --> 00:37:23,667
And so muscular!

423
00:37:23,875 --> 00:37:27,167
With steely veins running down…

424
00:37:27,625 --> 00:37:30,833
Hair sticking out like wire…

425
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:35,042
And those tough toenails!

426
00:37:35,208 --> 00:37:36,667
How many hills must it travel…

427
00:37:36,833 --> 00:37:38,208
How many seas must it pass…

428
00:37:38,375 --> 00:37:39,792
How much pain must it bear…

429
00:37:39,917 --> 00:37:44,875
Before a calf becomes a calf?

430
00:37:48,750 --> 00:37:51,583
I shall have this calf!

431
00:37:51,875 --> 00:37:52,917
Master!

432
00:37:57,125 --> 00:37:59,667
Can I take a pee?

433
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:07,250
Whenever I sing this song, I need to pee.

434
00:38:07,875 --> 00:38:11,375
Taking a pee first would not help.

435
00:38:11,875 --> 00:38:14,542
But I must sing it now.

436
00:38:14,708 --> 00:38:17,708
With this song, I hope…

437
00:38:18,125 --> 00:38:20,333
Logan will think better of me.

438
00:38:20,500 --> 00:38:22,958
Logan will be my master!

439
00:38:23,125 --> 00:38:25,917
The song goes like this…

440
00:38:26,042 --> 00:38:27,542
"Big bun, have two more…"

