"Forget about indigestion."

449
00:38:49,167 --> 00:38:54,333
"Eat the bun, grow a calf…"

450
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:57,542
"Respect my mother."

451
00:38:58,375 --> 00:39:03,750
"Eat the bun, toughen my calf…"

452
00:39:03,917 --> 00:39:07,333
"Serve my country."

453
00:39:08,458 --> 00:39:10,000
"Big bun, have two more…"

